IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. REFINE.

DATA DIVISION.

WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 REFINE-QTY     PIC 9(5).
01 REFINE-QTY-STR PIC X(5).
01 REQUIRED-ORE PIC 9(7).

LINKAGE SECTION.
01 LK-ORE-STOCK PIC 9(5).
01 LK-INGOT-STOCK PIC 9(5).

PROCEDURE DIVISION USING LK-ORE-STOCK LK-INGOT-STOCK.
  MOVE 0 TO REFINE-QTY
  MOVE SPACES TO REFINE-QTY-STR

  PERFORM UNTIL REFINE-QTY > 0
    DISPLAY "いくつ精錬しますか？(鉱石10個で1つ精錬)"
    DISPLAY "所持鉱石：" LK-ORE-STOCK "個"
    DISPLAY "所持インゴット：" LK-INGOT-STOCK "個"
    DISPLAY "キャンセルする場合は0を入力してください"
    ACCEPT REFINE-QTY-STR

    IF FUNCTION TRIM(REFINE-QTY-STR) IS NOT NUMERIC
      DISPLAY "数字を入力してください"
      MOVE 0 TO REFINE-QTY
    ELSE
      MOVE FUNCTION TRIM(REFINE-QTY-STR) TO REFINE-QTY

      IF REFINE-QTY = 0
        DISPLAY "キャンセルしました"
        EXIT PARAGRAPH
      END-IF

      IF REFINE-QTY > 1000
        DISPLAY "一度に精錬できるのは1,000個までです"
        MOVE 0 TO REFINE-QTY
      END-IF
    END-IF
  END-PERFORM

  COMPUTE REQUIRED-ORE = REFINE-QTY * 10

  IF LK-ORE-STOCK >= REQUIRED-ORE
    ADD REFINE-QTY TO LK-INGOT-STOCK
    SUBTRACT REQUIRED-ORE FROM LK-ORE-STOCK
    DISPLAY REFINE-QTY "個のインゴットを精製しました！"
    DISPLAY "所持鉱石：" LK-ORE-STOCK "個"
    DISPLAY "所持インゴット：" LK-INGOT-STOCK "個"
  ELSE
    DISPLAY "鉱石が足りません"
  END-IF

  GOBACK.
